metadata.name: Eternal Evolution
metadata.description:
The process of levitating and falling,
Is the process of the soul's elevation,
A journey towards the heavens,
Or a descent into manifestation.

With each rise, the soul ascends,
Its essence reaching for the divine,
While with each fall, it descends,
To experience the earthly confines.

But through it all, the celestial light,
Guides the way, shining ever so bright,
A beacon of hope in times of despair,
Reminding us that our soul's journey is rare.

So let this artwork be a reminder,
That our souls are always in a state of wonder,
Levitating and falling, rising and descending,
On a journey of growth, towards an eternal ending.
